<plot>This film explores the life and work of Michael Scott, one of Ireland's foremost architects and the father of director Ciarin Scott. His journey through life takes the film through the tumultuous forging of Ireland's independence and the drive to bring the country into the modern world of the visual arts.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?368409</url></doc>
